channel.description:
Since first starting out this channel, the idea has changed a bit now that the UK has had a general election in May 2010.

However, with a coalition government between the Conservatives and Liberal Democrats, there is still lots of muck to be released about the Labour government, and new muck from the coalition.

The broadcasters would normally junk these clips and never show them again (hoard in their archives). This channel makes it possible to see a fraction of what the scumbag politicians don't want you to remember they said or did.

Feb 14 2010, 1000th (non deleted) clip
Feb 12 2012, 2000th (non deleted) clip
